Interface BaseGraph<G extends GraphHead,V extends Vertex,E extends Edge,LG extends BaseGraph<G,V,E,LG,GC>,GC extends BaseGraphCollection<G,V,E,LG,GC>>

  • Type Parameters:
    G - type of the graph head
    V - the vertex type
    E - the edge type
    LG - the type of the logical graph that will be created with a provided factory
    GC - the type of the graph collection that will be created with a provided factory
